      - - edit
        - fileRegex: (EXTRACTION-.*\.md$|VERIFICATION-.*\.md$|DOCS-TEMP-.*\.md$|\.roo/docs-extractor/.*\.md$)
          description: Extraction/Verification report files only (source-material), plus legacy DOCS-TEMP
